<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { title, description }) %>
</head>
<body class="bg-page text-text-primary font-body antialiased overflow-x-hidden">
  <canvas id="dot-grid" class="fixed inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div id="cursor-glow" class="fixed w-[320px] h-[320px] rounded-full pointer-events-none z-0 opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59,130,246,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); transform: translate(-50%, -50%);" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <main class="relative z-10 pt-20">
    <section class="py-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-accent/20 bg-accent/10 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">AI Audit</span>
        <h1 class="mt-8 text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-black tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">We'll show you exactly where your business is leaking time and money, and what's worth fixing first.</h1>
        <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
          A free 30-minute working session. We walk through your operation, find where things are getting lost, and come out with a clear picture of the highest-leverage fix.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 text-sm text-text-secondary">
          <span class="rounded-full border border-border-subtle px-4 py-2">30 minutes</span>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-border-subtle px-4 py-2">Free</span>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-border-subtle px-4 py-2">No obligation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10">
          <a href="https://calendly.com/cosminlungu/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Book Your AI Audit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="glass-card p-8" data-tilt>
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent text-white font-display font-bold">1</div>
            <h2 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-display font-bold">Map the workflow</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">We walk through how work actually moves in your business. Leads, assignments, communication, the places where everything routes through you personally.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-8" data-tilt>
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent text-white font-display font-bold">2</div>
            <h2 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-display font-bold">Find the leaks</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">Deals that go cold, tasks that vanish, follow-up that depends on memory. We find what's costing the most and name it clearly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-8" data-tilt>
            <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent text-white font-display font-bold">3</div>
            <h2 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-display font-bold">Recommend the fix</h2>
            <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">You leave with a specific picture of what to build, in what order, and what implementation looks like for your business.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="glass-card border border-accent/30 p-8 lg:p-10">
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Good fit</span>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>You run a real business with real operational complexity</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>You want a clear picture of what to build, not a sales pitch</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>You suspect time or revenue is leaking somewhere</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-accent"></span><span>You want to leave the call with a concrete next step</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="glass-card p-8 lg:p-10">
            <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-text-muted">Not ideal</span>
            <ul class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-text-muted"></span><span>You want a broad conversation about AI trends</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-text-muted"></span><span>You're not ready to talk about specific operations or problems</span></li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-text-muted"></span><span>You're expecting a hard sales pitch</span></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="pb-section-sm lg:pb-section">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="glass-card p-10 lg:p-14 text-center">
          <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4">No Strings Attached</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">This is not a vague sales call.</h2>
          <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">
            The point is clarity. If the right answer is "don't build this yet," I'll say that. If there's a strong case, you'll know exactly why before the call ends.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10">
            <a href="https://calendly.com/cosminlungu/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex rounded-xl bg-accent px-8 py-4 text-white font-semibold transition-colors hover:bg-accent-hover" data-magnetic>Reserve Your Spot</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/dot-grid.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/nav.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/magnetic.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/tilt.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
